main.tf - Orchestration Layer
================================

Purpose: Acts as the conductor, importing and configuring the VPC module

Key Feature: Uses a remote Git repository for the VPC module (version-controlled infrastructure as code)

provider.tf - Cloud Connection
=========================================
State Management: Uses S3 backend with encryption and lockfiles

Provider Version: Pinned to AWS provider v6.16.0 for stability

variables.tf - Configuration Parameters
=======================================
Smart Defaults: Pre-configured CIDR ranges and naming

Three-tier CIDR Strategy:

Public: 10.0.1.0/24, 10.0.2.0/24

Private: 10.0.11.0/24, 10.0.12.0/24

Database: 10.0.21.0/24, 10.0.22.0/24


VPC Module Components (vpc.tf, data.tf, locals.tf)
=============================================

