         Consistent Naming: Generates names like roboshop-dev-public-us-east-1a

         Tagging Strategy: Every resource gets standardized tags

---> data.tf - Environment Discovery

          Fetches available AZs dynamically

          Discovers default VPC and main route table from AWS

---> vpc.tf - Resource Blueprint

         VPC: DNS hostnames enabled for internal resolution

         Subnets: Three distinct tiers across two AZs

          Route Tables: Isolated routing per tier

         Intelligent Merging: Custom tags + common tags + name tags


